&lt;p&gt;At Ernest, our merchandisers (we call them merchandisers because, well, they do &lt;em&gt;a lot&lt;/em&gt; more than just purchase) help shape the partnerships, pricing, and performance that drive our business forward. We’re looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Merchandiser&lt;/strong&gt; to join our team, &lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;where you’ll play a vital role in ensuring our customers receive quality solutions, competitive pricing, and exceptional service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full-time, on-site position for someone who’s skilled at &lt;strong&gt;building vendor relationships&lt;/strong&gt;, identifying &lt;strong&gt;cost-saving opportunities&lt;/strong&gt;, and managing product lines with a high degree of ownership and attention to detail. If you&#39;re organized, collaborative, and enjoy working cross-functionally to deliver results — this could be your next step.&lt;/p&gt;
